description:
Crypto Warriors (CZ) is the world's first block chain game combining 3D RPG and Mining content.

The higher the level-up, the better the item is, the higher the profitability, and the limited number of CZ tokens can be preoccupied every day. CryptoWarrior's collaboration with the Matic Network has implemented the NFT system in the game and enables the transaction of items between users in the game. Crypto Warriors (CZ) will also collaborate with HDac to expand our business and collaborate on technology.In the future, infrastructure expansion and development collaboration will be carried out through multiple partnerships. CZ tokens are used to purchase various items in the game, participate in Daejeon content, and pay for advertising execution in the Krypto Warrior's game.
name: CryptowarriorZ
